										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>For the release of one ERU, in ERRS (Electronic Remote Release Systems) for Liferafts, EPIRBs or Lifebuoys. The Release Switch, Flush mount is used for integration to a panel inside a weather-protected area. The components are the same parts as those installed in <a href="https://www.cmhammar.com/catalogue/hm-0550/">HM-0550</a>.</p>
<p>Includes:</p>
<ul>
<li>Release Switch module and an</li>
<li>Electronic switch module.</li>
</ul>
<p>The electronic switch module has two fastening holes and shall be mounted protected on the inside of the instrument panel.</p>
